  "title": "Cobblemon: Poke Stops",
  "description": "Add pokemon stops with healing machine and pc.",
  "body": "<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Cobblemon : Simple Pokestop's</h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_997832fd-11b4-4335-b260-dea3ebf2cb44.png\" width=\"404\" height=\"404\"></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.7.1-Cobblemon-brightgreen\" width=\"139\" height=\"24\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/architectury-api\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/13.0.8-ArchitecturyAPI-red\" width=\"168\" height=\"24\"></a> <a href=\"https://neoforged.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.21.1-NeoForge-darkred\" width=\"125\" height=\"24\"></a> <a href=\"https://fabricmc.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.21.1-Fabric-blue\" width=\"103\" height=\"24\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemore-library\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.2.7 -CobblemoreLib-purple\" width=\"165\" height=\"24\"></a></p>\n<p><strong>◽ Have you ever been in the middle of a journey and had nowhere to heal your pokemons?</strong><br><strong>◽ This is a simple mod that adds a pokemon stops with some berries, a healing machine and a computer.<br></strong></p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>◽ To configure the spawn distance between buildings, you must open the mod's &ldquo;Jar&rdquo; file, go to -&gt;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ced4d9;\">data/cobblemon_poke_stopsr/worldgen/structure_set/poke_stops.json</span>. &nbsp;Inside it, change &lsquo;<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">spacing</span>&rsquo; and &ldquo;<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">separation</span>.&rdquo;<br></strong></p>\n<p><strong>◽ To configure the biomes where the building will appear, you will need to open the mod's &ldquo;Jar&rdquo; file, go to -&gt; <span style=\"color: #ced4d9;\">data/cobblemon_poke_stops/tags/worldgen/biome/has_structure/poke_stops.json</span>. Inside it, change the biomes according to the tags, for example <span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">#c:is_forest.</span></strong></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>My other mods:&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon-create-industries\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Neoforge-Fabric-blue\" alt=\"\" width=\"127\" height=\"24\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon-create-industries\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.21.1 | 1.20.1-Cobblemon Industries-purple\" width=\"278\" height=\"24\"></a>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon-additions-tools\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Neoforge-Fabric-blue\" alt=\"\" width=\"127\" height=\"24\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon-additions-tools\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.21.1 | 1.20.1-Cobblemon : Tools-purple\" width=\"252\" height=\"24\"></a>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon-poke-labs\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Neoforge-Fabric-blue\" alt=\"\" width=\"127\" height=\"24\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon-poke-labs\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.21.1 | 1.20.1-Cobblemon : Poke Labs-purple\" width=\"283\" height=\"24\"></a>&nbsp;<br></strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemore-library\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Neoforge-Fabric-blue\" alt=\"\" width=\"127\" height=\"24\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemore-library\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.21.1 | 1.20.1-Cobblemore Lib-purple\" width=\"230\" height=\"24\"></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/NeoForge-purple\" alt=\"\" width=\"76\" height=\"24\"> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon-botany-pots\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.21.1-Cobblemon : Botany Pots-purple\" width=\"236\" height=\"24\"></a>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<hr>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>Credit model : @<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/styrix/\" rel=\"nofollow\">styrix</a></h3>",
